POST http://localhost:8000/turmas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Teste Turma",
  "capacidade": 20
}

### Listar alunos
GET http://localhost:8000/alunos

### Criar aluno
POST http://localhost:8000/alunos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Aluno Teste",
  "data_nascimento": "2010-01-01",
  "email": "teste@email.com",
  "status": "ativo",
  "turma_id": 1
}

### Editar aluno
PUT http://localhost:8000/alunos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Aluno Editado",
  "data_nascimento": "2010-01-01",
  "email": "editado@email.com",
  "status": "ativo",
  "turma_id": 1
}

### Deletar aluno
DELETE http://localhost:8000/alunos/1

### Matricular aluno
POST http://localhost:8000/matriculas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "aluno_id": 2,
  "turma_id": 1
}
